Continuing from the comment, let&#39;s consider a real world scenario (using a, c, d... can be tough and misleading):

```java

package com.example.animals; // com/example/animals/Lion.java
public class Lion {
}


package com.example.zoo; // com/example/zoo/Zoo.java
public class Zoo {
    public class Lion {
    }
}
```

